If He come & ye (Quakers) bide none other, why do we hear at all your
meetings, especially when these are most godly, as you say. the voice
of sobbing, of weeping, lamentation, yea anguish, sorrow, pain &
ululation as for one dead? Is this the jubilant voice of the bride for
her bridegroom?
